name: City of Surrey City Hall
directions:
Main floor of City Hall has two non-gendered individual bathrooms just east of the main entrance on 104 Ave
Just west of the gendered washrooms is a single non gendered accessible washroom with a change table.
comment: Surrey City Hall is a safe choice for the neighbourhood.

name: Surrey City Hall
directions: Main floor atrium has 3 gender neutral single bathrooms. 1 offers accessibility and a change table.
comment: The atrium at Surrey City Hall is a safe environment for everyone. Access to both gendered and gender neutral bathrooms is open and available to anyone. A coffee shop, information/security desk and open layout, City Hall is your best bet for a safer space in the neighborhood.
